}

<h1 class="ds-page-title">Components</h1>
<p class="ds-page-lead">
    Reusable UI components for building consistent interfaces across COMPASS. Each component includes examples, usage guidelines, and code snippets.
</p>

<h2>Breadcrumb bar</h2>
<p>
