    </div>
</div>

<h2>Notification banner</h2>
<p>
    Notification banners alert users to important information or status updates.
</p>

<h3>Warning</h3>
<div class="component-example">
    <div class="component-example-title">Example</div>
    <div class="dfe-adminui-alert dfe-adminui-alert--warning" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <strong>Warning:</strong> This action cannot be undone.
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Info</h3>
<div class="component-example">
    <div class="component-example-title">Example</div>
    <div class="dfe-adminui-alert dfe-adminui-alert--info" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <strong>Information:</strong> Your changes have been saved.
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Success</h3>
<div class="component-example">
    <div class="component-example-title">Example</div>
    <div class="dfe-adminui-alert dfe-adminui-alert--success" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <strong>Success:</strong> The operation completed successfully.
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Danger / Error</h3>
<div class="component-example">
    <div class="component-example-title">Example</div>
    <div class="dfe-adminui-alert dfe-adminui-alert--danger" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <strong>Error:</strong> An error occurred. Please try again.
    </div>
</div>

<h2>Component usage guidelines</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Use components consistently across all COMPASS features</li>
    <li>Follow accessibility guidelines for each component</li>
    <li>Test components with keyboard navigation and screen readers</li>
    <li>Ensure components are responsive and work on all screen sizes</li>
    <li>Maintain visual consistency with existing COMPASS pages</li>
</ul>
